citation: Straits Islands Shipping Services Subsidies Act (Repeal) Act 1995 (Tas)
text:
Straits Islands Shipping Services Subsidies Act (Repeal) Act 1995

An Act to repeal the Straits Islands Shipping Services Subsidies Act 1948
[Royal Assent 14 November 1995]

Be it enacted by His Excellency the Governor of Tasmania, by and with the advice and consent of the Legislative Council and House of Assembly, in Parliament assembled, as follows:

1. Short title
    This Act may be cited as the Straits Islands Shipping Services Subsidies Act (Repeal) Act 1995 .

2. Commencement
    This Act commences on a day to be proclaimed.

3. Repeal
    The Straits Islands Shipping Services Subsidies Act 1948 is repealed.
